{"tid":1706861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"推唔推十月十二日繼續三罷","createTime":"2019-11-11T07:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T07:43:45.000Z","uid":46984,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eee091b497211aced04dce531c9bf534a8e9837d","tid":1706861,"uid":46984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:37:39.000Z","msg":"聽日好似未有定案<br />\n全香港全部黃絲罷工都應該夠做<br />\n<br />\n希望黃絲上司/老闆放風支持或者幫幫手帶頭罷工<br />\n有第一間就有第二間架啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇人/唔夠時間罷又有小朋友出黎抗爭受傷</span><br />\n每個人做少少佢地起碼唔洗又跪又盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋見有POST推八大永久罷課<br />\nD狗沖入大學都係唔想大家返學咁不如大家都唔好返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外今日有太多事<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">手足中槍同警犬亂撞人既post都開始沉</span><br />\n麻煩各位係FB 同IG 最起碼都推一推返上黎<br />\n火魔法要留意 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不過警犬變本加厲都唔可以由佢沉</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">之前開post都係自己推唔上 我自己推多幾次<br />\n都係一樣唔岩聽就由佢沉</span>"},{"pid":"957413f66eaf98eb56477fee667c02ae7d10f580","tid":1706861,"uid":46984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:40:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7db97305a22974b0e28eb794c0dee441862734ce","tid":1706861,"uid":46984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:41:40.000Z","msg":"今晚大家返屋企先?<br />\n留力聽日留係屋企做家務<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b5d8748ead5cd0731fa7876623ba073154bd83","tid":1706861,"uid":309248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:42:53.000Z","msg":"11月"},{"pid":"fbb915b3311dee3fccba48f9c372cef8deb1da66","tid":1706861,"uid":46984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:43:45.000Z","msg":"仆街開過先<br />\n屌"}]}